    "Fry graduated from King's College, Cambridge, with firsts in natural sciences, 1887 and 1888.": [],
    "Partially to please his father he dabbled in scientific areas while studying studio painting on the side.": [],
    "Entirely won over to art, he traveled to Italy in 1891 and studied studio painting at the Acad\u00e9mie Julian, Paris in 1892.": [
