    "Returning to Italy and resolving to study art history, he read the works of <a href=\"/morellig\">Giovanni Morelli</a> on connoisseurship and <a href=\"/paterw\">Walter Pater</a>.": [],
    "His acquaintance with the scholar <a href=\"/berensonb\">Bernard Berenson</a> likely happened during this time.": [],
    "Fry soon established a reputation as a scholar of Italian art, lecturing on the subject for the Cambridge Extension Movement.": [],
